            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-3">
              Obligations to remove or block the use of information under general laws remain unaffected.
              However, liability in this regard is only possible from the time of knowledge of a specific legal violation.
              Upon becoming aware of such violations, we will remove this content immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
